                            </p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">Laravel</span>
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">7 dias
                                    grátis</span>
